long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
This is a simple three-point shooting contest game where you control Bugs Bunny. You get up to 1 minute to shoot 25 shots from 5 different shooting racks. Make the money ball at the end of each rack for double points
